Case Statements - 


7) We want to Say that If a Course is Less Than 4 Months It is a "DIPLOMA"  ELSE It is a "MASTERS"

SELECT courses_id, course_name, fees, 
CASE 
WHEN duration > 4 THEN 'masters'
ELSE 'diploma'
END as course_type
FROM courses;


OR 

SELECT course_id, course_name, fees, CASE WHEN duration > 4 THEN 'masters' ELSE 'diploma' END as course_type FROM courses;




+-----------+-----------------+------------+-------------+
| course_id | course_name     | course_fee | course_type |
+-----------+-----------------+------------+-------------+
|         1 | web development |      45000 | masters     |
|         2 | DevOps          |      55000 | masters     |
|         3 | data science    |      40000 | masters     |
|         4 | bigdata         |      42000 | masters     |
|         5 | aws             |      15000 | diploma     |
+-----------+-----------------+------------+-------------+








